PLEASE HELP ME ANSWERING THIS QUESTION: How do I change the color of text using CSS? 

 COURSE CONTENT: Introduction to CSS 
 CSS (Cascading Style Sheets) is a style sheet language used for describing the look and formatting of a document written in HTML. 
 Example CSS: 
 body { 
 font-family: Arial, sans-serif; 
 margin: 0; 
 padding: 0; 
 } 
 h1 { 
 color: blue; 
 }

PLEASE HELP ME ANSWERING THIS QUESTION: What is the purpose of using the 'body' selector in CSS? 

 COURSE CONTENT: Example CSS: 
 body { 
